</em></em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 10: 1090XP\n<ul>\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n[/fancy-ul][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/3\"][heading subtitle=\"The Watcher; Applause Maker; Fear Banisher\"]Grandiok[/heading][vc_column_text]The great narrator god, Grandiok revels in the fantastic and is a master of spectacle.\n\nHis powers will embolden the cast, granting them the ability to act out in new and different ways, and occasionally gift them with wonderous new powers.[/vc_column_text][vc_text_separator title=\"Gains 1XP per Twitch Follower\"][fancy-ul icon_type=\"standard_dash\" color=\"Accent-Color\"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Level 0: 0XP\n<ul>\n	<li>We will find a fourth player</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 1: 10XP\n<ul>\n	<li>The live chat will choose from a list of (disappointingly) minor magic items to give one of the players</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 2: 50XP\n<ul>\n	<li>The GM will dress up in costume for the next game</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 3: 110XP\n<ul>\n	<li>A player character will be forced to adopt a behavior which the audience will choose from a list</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 4: 190XP\n<ul>\n	<li>Ability<em> ???</em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 5: 290XP\n<ul>\n	<li>Ability<em> <em><em>???</em></em></em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 6: 410XP\n<ul>\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 7: 550XP\n<ul>\n	<li>Keeper\'s costume will be in drag</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 8: 710XP\n<ul>\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 9: 890XP\n<ul>\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 10: 1090XP\n<ul>\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n[/fancy-ul][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/3\"][heading subtitle=\"The Giver; Provider; Art Father; Purse Master\"]Mokdo\'ey[/heading][vc_column_text]Grandfather Mokdo\'ey, loved by artists in all lands that he is know.\n\nHe provides to those who create, and watches on lovingly but quietly, all while repairing stages, handing lights, preparing food and providing succor after shows and events.\n\nHis abilities surround supporting the other gods, allowing them to work further, longer and more often. Without his support the other gods would be be unable to rouse to their greatest of feats.[/vc_column_text][vc_text_separator title=\"Gains 1XP per Patreon Subscriber\"][fancy-ul icon_type=\"standard_dash\" color=\"Accent-Color\"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Level 0: 0XP\n<ul>\n	<li>We will release games as audio podcasts</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 1: 10XP\n<ul>\n	<li>Our writers will produce and publish a cursed magic item influenced by audience suggestions</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 2: 50XP\n<ul>\n	<li>Our artists will create portraits of the player characters</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 3:\n<ul>\n	<li>Our writers will produce and publish an NPC influenced by audience suggestions</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 4: 190XP\n<ul>\n	<li>Our artists will depict a scene involving the characters and influenced by audience suggestions</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 5: 290XP\n<ul>\n	<li>Our production crew will edit games to be published on Youtube with superior presentation.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 6: 410XP\n<ul>\n	<li>Mokdo\'ey will double Despia\'s donation to charity!</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 7: 550XP\n<ul>\n	<li>Our writers will produce and publish an adventure influenced by audience suggestions</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 8: 710XP\n<ul>\n	<li>Grandiok\'s XP will count for double!!</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 9: 890XP\n<ul>\n	<li>Our writers will produce an entire DCC module influenced by audience suggestions</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>Level 10: 1090XP\n<ul>\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n[/fancy-ul][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"in_container\" scene_position=\"center\" text_color=\"dark\" text_align=\"left\" overlay_strength=\"0.3\"][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]This progression is in flux and may change up until the show begins, and mystery unlocks will be revealed as they are approached.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','The Keep Studios Presents: Audience Character Advancement','','inherit','closed','closed','','143-autosave-v1','','','2016-01-11 04:58:55','2016-01-11 04:58:55','',143,'http://thekeepstudios.com/2015/10/02/143-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(152,3,'2015-10-02 15:49:50','2015-10-02 15:49:50','[vc_row type=\"in_container\" scene_position=\"center\" text_color=\"dark\" text_align=\"left\"][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/3\"][heading subtitle=\"Lady of Music; Change Queen; Bards\' Muse\"]Despia[/heading][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/3\"][heading subtitle=\"The Watcher; The Laughter from the Dark; Applause Maker; Fear Banisher\"]Grandiok[/heading][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/3\"][heading subtitle=\"The Giver; Provider; Art Father; Purse Master\"]Mokdo\'ey[/heading][/vc_column][/vc_row]','The Keep Studios Presents #1: Audience Character Advancement','','inherit','closed','closed','','143-revision-v1','','','2015-10-02 15:49:50','2015-10-02 15:49:50','',143,'http://thekeepstudios.com/2015/10/02/143-revision-v1/',0,'revision',''