=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/3\"][image_with_animation image_url=\"139\" alignment=\"center\" animation=\"Fade In\" img_link_target=\"_blank\" img_link=\"http://twitch.com/thekeepstudios\"][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/3\"][fancy-ul icon_type=\"standard_dash\" color=\"Accent-Color\"]\n<ul>\n	<li>When: October 3rd, 2015 at 7PM EST (UTC-5)</li>\n	<li>Where:  <a href=\"http://www.twitch.tv/thekeepstudios\" target=\"_blank\">www.twitch.tv/thekeepstudios</a></li>\n	<li>Why: To have fun playing D&amp;D and help <a href=\"http://www.kaboom.org\" target=\"_blank\">\"Kaboom!\"</a></li>\n</ul>\n[/fancy-ul][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"in_container\" scene_position=\"center\" text_color=\"dark\" text_align=\"left\"][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/1\"][vc_text_separator title=\"Fear not! The Keep Studios provides!\"][vc_column_text]On October 3rd, 2015 at 7PM EST (UTC -5) on <a href=\"http://www.twitch.tv/thekeepstudios\" target=\"_blank\">The Keep Studios\' Twitch Channel</a> we will be hosting a live <span class=\"inline-comment-marker valid\">old school style D&amp;D</span> game using the wicked, ridiculous and stupendous Dungeon Crawl Classics RPG rules. Our adventures will take us through dark and daring tales with both fantasy and sci-fi in the vein of sword and sorcery classics.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nOur players are Ian “Jazz” Maur, our resident sound engineer and jaunty fellow; our dear friend and occasional intern Benjamin “Pointblank” Mishler, a Purdue Aerospace Engineering student and adorable scamp; and the delightful Jake \"Greshic\" Callaghan who makes incredible one-of-a-kind jewelry - and gloriously extravagant hilarity - on-demand. They will be lead through trouble and toil by The Keep Studios CEO and resident madman Ian “Keeper” Small.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWe\'ll be trying to raise awareness and funding for the <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://kaboom.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">\"Kaboom!\"</a>charity which shares our philosophy that play is an important part of life - at every stage of life, but especially childhood - and should be encouraged where possible.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nThis is where YOU come in. The audience will be able to level up three great deities, unlocking powers such as giveaways, future games, and the ever dreaded Audience Participation Abilitieswhere our live viewers will be able to change the world IN REAL TIME to mess with both the players and the dungeon master.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nDetails on the deities, how to gain XP for them and their abilities will be released throughout the week prior to the game.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','The Keep Studios Presents','','inherit','closed','closed','','135-autosave-v1','','','2015-10-02 23:28:58','2015-10-02 23:28:58','',135,'http://thekeepstudios.com/2015/10/02/135-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(164,6,'2015-10-02 23:29:01','2015-10-02 23:29:01','[vc_row type=\"in_container\" scene_position=\"center\" text_color=\"dark\" text_align=\"left\"][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]Hello lovely internet people!\r\n\r\nDon\'t you love watching a bunch of nerdy game developers pretend to be great burly warriors and cunning rogues in fantastic tales of adventure; all while being victimized by cold, soulless dice? What\'s that I hear you say? \"Yes yes, but I’d much rather be involved in their plight, like a mad god dictating capricious and mercurial whims from on high, casting down plights and blessings and blessings alike upon them.\"\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" co