m>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 9: 890XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 10: 1090XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fancy-ul][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/3\"][heading subtitle=\"The Giver; Provider; Art Father; Purse Master\"]Mokdo\'ey[/heading][vc_column_text]Grandfather Mokdo\'ey, loved by artists in all lands that he is know.\r\n\r\nHe provides to those who create, and watches on lovingly but quietly, all while repairing stages, handing lights, preparing food and providing succor after shows and events.\r\n\r\nHis abilities surround supporting the other gods, allowing them to work further, longer and more often. Without his support the other gods would be be unable to rouse to their greatest of feats.[/vc_column_text][vc_text_separator title=\"Gains 1XP per Patreon Subscriber\"][fancy-ul icon_type=\"standard_dash\" color=\"Accent-Color\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Level 0: 0XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We will release games as audio podcasts</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 1: 10XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Our writers will produce and publish a cursed magic item influenced by audience suggestions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 2: 50XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Our artists will create portraits of the player characters</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 3:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Our writers will produce and publish an NPC influenced by audience suggestions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 4: 190XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Our artists will depict a scene involving the characters and influenced by audience suggestions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 5: 290XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Our production crew will edit games to be published on Youtube with superior presentation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 6: 410XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mokdo\'ey will double Despia\'s donation to charity!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 7: 550XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Our writers will produce and publish an adventure influenced by audience suggestions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 8: 710XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Grandiok\'s XP will count for double!!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 9: 890XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Our writers will produce an entire DCC module influenced by audience suggestions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 10: 1090XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fancy-ul][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"in_container\" scene_position=\"center\" text_color=\"dark\" text_align=\"left\" overlay_strength=\"0.3\"][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]This progression is in flux and may change up until the show begins, and mystery unlocks will be revealed as they are approached.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','The Keep Studios Presents: Audience Character Advancement','','inherit','closed','closed','','143-revision-v1','','','2016-02-04 16:47:02','2016-02-04 16:47:02','',143,'http://thekeepstudios.com/2016/02/04/143-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(200,9,'2016-05-05 02:53:29','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Meet the Team','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2016-05-05 02:53:29','2016-05-05 02:53:29','',0,'http://thekeepstudios.com/?page_id=200',0,'page','',0),(201,9,'2016-05-05 02:53:29','2016-05-05 02:53:29','','Meet the Team','','inherit','closed','closed','','200-revision-v1','','','2016-05-05 02:53:29','2016-05-05 02:53:29','',200,'http://thekeepstudios.com/2016/05/05/200-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(202,3,'2016-10-02 18:47:54','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-10-02 18:47:54','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://thekeepstudios.com/?p=202',0,'post','',0),(203,3,'2016-10-02 18:4